Download "NohBoard-ReWrite-v1.3.0.zip"
Extract and then run the executable
Download "Hazard.style" and place in "keyboards/joao7yt/fps/"
In NohBoard, right click and select "Load Keyboard"
Choose "joao7yt" as category and "Hazard" as Keyboard Style.

In StreamLabs, add source as "Window Capture"
Select NohBoard as the window and click "Done"
Right Click on source and click "Filters"
Click the plus icon to add a filter and add filter type "Chroma Key"
Click "Done" and then edit the chroma key settings if needed (should not need to).
Click "Done" and enjoy.
